N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 15 ยง 91.4 - Exclusions

State Regulations
(a) This Part shall
not apply to tickets issued within any city having a population of one million
or over for offenses occurring therein. (b) Uniform traffic tickets shall not be
issued for parking, stopping or standing violations. Notes
